respec only - Run specs only on files matching a pattern

Alias: o

[1mUsage:[0m
  respec only SEARCH [OPTIONS]
  respec only --help | -h

[1mOptions:[0m
  --watch, -w
    Watch for change and rerun
    Conflicts: --repeat

  --repeat, -r
    Wait for a key press after running and repeat
    Conflicts: --watch

  --help, -h
    Show this help

[1mArguments:[0m
  SEARCH
    Partial filename

[1mExamples:[0m
  # run specs only on paths matching '*integration*'
  $ respec only integration
